# React Component Standards

## Component Structure
- Use functional components with TypeScript
- Implement proper prop typing using interfaces
- Export components as default when they are the main export
- Use named exports for utility components

## Component Props
- Define prop interfaces with 'Props' suffix (e.g., ButtonProps)
- Use proper prop validation
- Implement default props using destructuring
- Document complex props with JSDoc comments

## Accessibility
- Implement proper ARIA attributes
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Ensure keyboard navigation support
- Include proper focus management
- Add proper alt texts for images

